<plot>In this edition of RKO's "Pal" series, Gary loses his dog, Pal (Flame the Wonder Dog), when his father sells Pal to a film company. Lonesome for his young master, Pal runs away from his new owners and makes the long trip back to Gary. The film director, aware that Pal is useless as an animal actor without his young master, signs Gary to a film contract.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?420775</url></doc>
